fields.title: Dossier API – updateSchemaSpecification
fields.description: Learn how to use updateSchemaSpecification to make changes to the schema with the Dossier API

children.text: is used to make changes to the schema. Most changes can be made by defining the intended changed schema (i.e. the API is declarative, not imperative). However, for some changes (e.g. renaming a type or a field) you need to also define a migration for Dossier to make the intended changes.
